title: Phoenician cemetery at al-Bass
description: Cemetery at the Al-Bass site in Tyre containing burials, funerary urns, and stelae dated to the Phoenician period (8th-6th century BCE).

properties.description: Point representing the imagery location of the Phoencian cemetery at al-Bass, derived from an OpenStreetMap Node after Aubet 2004.
